# typescript基本数据类型

### 1. boolean类型
```
text.bold = true;
```
### 2. number类型
```
text.textColor = 0xffffff;
```
### 3. string类型
```
text.textFlow = new Array<egret.ITextElement>(
    { text:"这段文字有链接", style: { "href" : "event:text event triggered", underline:true } }, 
    { text:"\n这段文字没链接", style: {"textColor" : 0x999999} }
);
```










